quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  45,1,"Ha, Mim."
  45,2,"Okhwishibwa khweshitabu shino khurula khu Nyasaye Owaamani, Owamachesi muno."
  45,3,"Toto khulikulu nende khushialo biliwo ebimanyisio khubalia basuubila."
  45,4,"Nende mukhuloongwa khwenyu, nende tsisolo tsiayaswaania, ebimanyisio bilimwo khubandu basuubilanga muno."
  45,5,"Ne okhubusania khweshilo nende eshitere nende omukabo kwa Nyasaye yeshinjia okhurula hekulu, mana nalamusia khukwo eshialo okhurula mulifwa liashio, nende okhubotokhana khwomuyeka, ebimanyisio bilimwo khubandu bekhonyelanga obwongo."
  45,6,"Tsino ni tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye khukhusomelanga khubwatoto, ne makhuwa shina kabanyala okhusuubila nikalali ka Nyasaye nende ebimanyisio bibie tawe?"
  45,7,"Eshinyasio eshikhongo shilinyoola buli omubeyi po, wetsimbi muno."
  45,8,"Awulilanga tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye nitsisomwa khulwa ye, niyekhulumamia khukalia kayakaywa, niyelola opara mbu shaatsiwulilekhwo tawe. Kho musuubisie eshinyasio eshilulu."
  45,9,"Ne namanya eshindu shiosishiosi mutsinyaali tsiefu nashikhonga okhuba omubayo. Abandu abo nibo baliba nende eshinyasio shiokhututuyibwa."
  45,10,"Inyuma wabu ni Jahannam, kabakhola shikalibakhoonya shiosishiosi tawe, nohomba balia babakhola okhuba abalindi, ne baliba neshinyasio eshikhongo."
  45,11,"Buno ni obulunjifu, ne balia bakhaya ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi balinyoola eshinyasio eshilulu eshibii."
  45,12,"Nyasaye niye wakhola inyanza ibarumushile kho ebininwa bichendemwo khubunyali bubwe, ne kho mukhaabemwo omukabo kukwe, kho munyoole okhupa orio."
  45,13,"Niye wakhola bibarumushile ebili mwikulu nende mushialo bioosi okhurula khuye. Toto mu ako bilimwo ebimanyisio khubandu baparanga."